name: Artículos mas Vendidos
query:
SELECT `tabSales Invoice Item`.`item_code` AS `item_code`, sum(`tabSales Invoice Item`.`qty`) AS `sum`
FROM `tabSales Invoice Item`
WHERE (`tabSales Invoice Item`.`docstatus` = 1)
GROUP BY `tabSales Invoice Item`.`item_code`
ORDER BY `sum` DESC, `tabSales Invoice Item`.`item_code` ASC
LIMIT 10
